title: Joseph Loduca.2013.SPARTACUS - WAR OF THE DAMNED SOUNDTRACKS[Mp3
description:
Joseph LoDuca - SPARTACUS: WAR OF THE DAMNED [SOUNDTRACKS] (2013)


Original soundtrack score to the final season of the Spartacus series composed by Joseph LoDuca. The series was inspired by the historical figure of Spartacus (played by Liam McIntyre), a Thracian gladiator who, from 73 to 71 BCE, led a major slave uprising against the Roman Republic.
